title: User Kernel keeps crashing
body:
Hi guys i havent played league in a while and i try to get back on to play it and my User Kernel crashes every time i try to join a game.
i can log in fine and that but when i try to connect it crashes. I reopen the game and it says im missing files and i need to retreive them. I finish the update and try to reconnect to the game again and it cashes. This just keeps repeating PLEASE HELP
